@ Kubectl VS Helm

------------------------------------
| Feature     | kubectl   | Helm   |
| ----------- | -------   | -----  |
| Deploy apps | Yes       | Yes    |
| Templating  | âŒ No    | âœ… Yes |
| Rollback    | âŒ No    | âœ… Yes |
| Versioning  | âŒ No    | âœ… Yes |
------------------------------------


@ Nginx Vs Ingress

-------------------------------------------------------------------
| Feature          | NGINX                 | Ingress              |
| ---------------- | --------------------- | -------------------- |
| Type             | Software              | Kubernetes object    |
| Purpose          | Serve & route traffic | Define routing rules |
| Runs where       | VM, server, container | Inside Kubernetes    |
| Handles traffic  | âœ… Yes                | âŒ No               |
| Needs controller | âŒ No                 | âœ… Yes              |
| Example          | Reverse proxy         | `/app â†’ service`     |
--------------------------------------------------------------------



